{"tid":2216242,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國律師管理局將聆訊是否剔除何君堯註冊律師資格","createTime":"2020-09-24T13:54:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T18:25:44.000Z","uid":79563,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"124773fc5c27ef9c691cc871628198b8222fb45d","tid":2216242,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T13:54:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551486-20200924.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551486-20200924.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=9ac1b758\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551486-20200924.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3289f457\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551486-20200924.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國保守黨人權委員會委員裴倫德，在社交網站Twitter表示，英國律師管理局將排期聆訊，決定是否從註冊律師名冊，剔除本港立法會議員何君堯。<br />\n<br />\n英國律師管理局回覆本台查詢時確認，事務律師紀律審裁處將分別在下月20日和12月14日，召開聆訊處理有關問題。<br />\n<br />\n裴倫德曾經去信何君堯母校英國安格利亞魯斯金大學，大學其後褫奪其名譽博士學位，律師管理局其後接獲投訴，指何君堯涉嫌違反專業要求，因此展開調查。"},{"pid":"cbe00533fb064ae275576e8e7a3ee34bf471ca86","tid":2216242,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T14:05:21.000Z","msg":"何妖係721既搞手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac89c9feba861227f3b178f0b161fe0a8c08aab","tid":2216242,"uid":12558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T20:34:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkg